description: This file exports a single function getSupabaseEnv that reads specific environment variables related to Supabase configuration from the React runtime environment (process.env). The function returns an object with url and key properties, representing the Supabase URL and API key, respectively.

methods.name: getSupabaseEnv()
methods.description: Reads Supabase environment variables from the React runtime environment and returns an object containing the URL and key.
